underlying_goal: Update the meeting link on a personal website.
primary_success: Identified that the website uses a centralized configuration pattern, explaining to the user that changing the link in `src/config.js` was sufficient to update it across the site.
brief_summary: The user asked to change a meeting link on their website. Claude located the link in `src/config.js`, updated it, and explained the project's centralized configuration pattern, where the link is defined once and reused.
